## version 2: 
- the model only show predictions of if hands are detected

# excecution of the application
- NOTE: all the relevent files are in "src" dir.
- clone this repo
- create a venv 
- install all the dependencies by running the following cmd in terminal.
        - $ pip install req.txt
- RUN the python script - capture_sign.py



# SIGN TO TEXT

- The model is trained on data with 250 classes (Gestures).
- Its is Tensor Flow lite model (TFLite), specially designed for smaller devices like mobile phones etc.
- 


## version 2: 
- the model only show predictions of if hands are detected